parameters:
Would you like to watch the event? Senpai's executive
entertainment.

\nc<Senpai>Then, let's work hard to finish today without any issues as
well.

\nc<Employee 1>Well, but we're on the better side. The team leader
distributes the work evenly...
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Just enough to barely meet our quotas.

\nc<Employee 3>Saki... if you exceed the quota too much, next term's quota
might triple, you know?

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>*cough* Now that you mention it, my quota is on a different
scale than when I was a newbie.

\nc<Employee 2>Really, they increase it arbitrarily. If it weren't for our
current team leader, we would have been sent on forced
dispatch long ago.

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>(Come to think of it, Meary-senpai's quota is at an
unbelievable level... How does she manage to meet it?)
